data.description: Come see this well maintained beautiful 2 story home in the desirable community of Canyon Hills. The home features an open floor plan with large  living room, high ceilings, a gourmet kitchen that includes granite countertops, built-in stainless steel appliances, center island, pantry, and plenty  of storage. The kitchen opens up to the dining room and family room with a fireplace. Downstairs you will also find an office or optional bedroom  and bathroom. The upstairs has a large master bedroom with a retreat area, master bathroom suite with dual sinks, separate shower/soaking tub,  and a large walk-in closet. Down the hallway are 3 more spacious bedrooms, bathroom with dual sinks, laundry room and a spacious loft. The  backyard is landscaped and has a concrete patio. The Canyon Hills planned community offers community pools/spa, tennis courts,  playgrounds, dog park and picnic areas. Very close to shopping, restaurants, entertainment and schools within walking distance.
